Q1. Write a python program to create a DataFrame from list of 10 integer values. Display contents of DataFrame and calculate sum, mean, median, mode, Standard deviation of DataFrame.


import pandas as pd
lst = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 20, 30, 40, 10, 60]
data = pd.DataFrame(lst, columns=["Numbers"])
print("DataFrame:\n", data)
print("\nSum:", data["Numbers"].sum())
print("Mean:", data["Numbers"].mean())
print("Median:", data["Numbers"].median())
print("Mode:\n", data["Numbers"].mode())
print("Standard Deviation:", data["Numbers"].std())


